Fus.24h.com.vn%252Ftin-van-bong-da%252Fchuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fus.24h.com.vn%252Ftin-van-bong-da%252Fchuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html%26correlator%3D1519425005%26ambient%3D1&ad_postrollOnly=0&ad_postrollTime=30&ad_postrollType=adsense&file=http://video-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/videoclip/2018-01-19/1516312124-jean-micha--l-seri.mp4&fileAlt=&image=http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-01-19/1516312124-jean-micha--l-seri.jpg&autoReEnableMini=1&volume=40&ad_volume=40&title=Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba?&ad_skipButton=1&mute=unmute&ad_mute=unmute&autoPlay=0\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"></div></div><!--end:str_video_player--></div><div id=\"pinListzplayer_78a351\" ></div><!--Begin:position_banner_sponsor_video--><!--End:position_banner_sponsor_video--><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_preroll\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_postroll\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_overlay\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_started\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_doi_tac\" style=\"display:none\"></div></div><!-- end_media_player \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nh\u1eafm \u201cYaya Toure m\u1edbi\u201d thay th\u1ebf Pogba</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd Daily Mirror, <strong>MU</strong> \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Paul Pogba khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 6 c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield (gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng) v\u00e0 Sevilla (Champions League) v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>MU</em>&nbsp;c\u0169ng v\u1eeba c\u1eed tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Nga theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Lokomotiv Moscow v\u00e0 Nice \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/16 Europa League h\u00f4m 22/2 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i Jean Michael-Seri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Xem-gio-dong-doi-trai-hu-Balotelli-de-the-cho-Pogba-reu_2390182-1519418487-829-width660height480.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Michael-Seri (Nice) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u201cYaya Toure m\u1edbi\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u201csi\u00eau qu\u1eady\u201d Mario Balotelli \u1edf Nice. Michael-Seri c\u0169ng t\u1eebng su\u00fdt c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 thay Pogba trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Nice hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S\u1eafp \u201ctr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u201d De Gea th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e2y vi\u1ebft uy t\u00edn Paul Hirst c\u1ee7a t\u1edd The Times v\u1eeba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng tin David De Gea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <u>MU</u> cho ph\u00e9p anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\u201d n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1edd b\u00e1o Ciaran Kelly c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Manchester Evening News th\u00ec cho bi\u1ebft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 220.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n khi cam k\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Xem-gio-dong-doi-trai-hu-Balotelli-de-the-cho-Pogba-a50536491b8214dec2f81a3c7128e100_crop_exact-1519418487-325-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">De Gea c\u1ee9u nguy cho MU tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u00f9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00e2u sao Tottenham</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd The Times cho hay, MU ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh London\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n anh v\u1ec1 \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Gia nh\u1eadp MU, Alderweireld c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u con s\u1ed1 75.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf Tottenham hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Martial \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i v\u00ec Sanchez</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh RMC Sport (Ph\u00e1p) \u0111\u01b0a tin cho bi\u1ebft Anthony Martial v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a AS Monaco \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Alexis Sanchez. Hi\u1ec7n Tottenham, Inter Milan v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i tin Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Martial, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Marcus Rashford \u1edf MU v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf khi Alexis Sanchez gia nh\u1eadp CLB n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 chi\u00eam lu\u00f4n su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i Ladbrokes \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra k\u00e8o tin r\u1eb1ng Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t cao 2/1 (\u0111\u1eb7t 1 \u0103n 2), theo sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 5/2 (\u0111\u1eb7t 2 \u0103n 5).</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU lo\u1ea1n v\u00ec Pogba - Mourinho: Si\u00eau c\u00f2 ra tay, Real &amp; Barca \u201dth\u1ea3 c\u00e2u\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-23/mu1-1519340839-8-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU lo\u1ea1n v\u00ec Pogba - Mourinho: Si\u00eau c\u00f2 ra tay, Real &amp; Barca \u201dth\u1ea3 c\u00e2u\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nh\u00e2n l\u00fac MU \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren, Real &amp; Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u201c\u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp\u201d Pogba.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html","id":"390"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 23/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/2: Gareth Bale l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940533\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-940533\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Gareth Bale l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real.</strong> Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Real 3 trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. T\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, trong 19 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a CLB, Bale kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn n\u1ed5i 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb AS (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Gareth Bale hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/2: Gareth Bale l\u00e0 &amp;#34;c\u00e1i gai&amp;#34; c\u1ee7a Real - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-22/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-23-2-Gareth-Bale-la-bale2-1519318747-969-width660height372.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian Real d\u00e0nh cho Bale \u0111ang s\u1eafp h\u1ebft</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mkhitaryan ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 Arsenal. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mkhitaryan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Arsenal. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u201ckh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp\u201d c\u1ee7a De Gea.</strong> Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Luis Muriel. Theo s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh (\u1edf c\u1ef1 ly 6 m\u00e9t) c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u1ea1t v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 48m/ph. Nh\u01b0ng De Gea ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 0,26 gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 (b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a m\u00e8o). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard \u0111\u00f2i Conte tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng</strong>. \u201cT\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khi ch\u01a1i r\u1ed9ng, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 do HLV \u0111\u01b0a ra, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d Hazard chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca gi\u1ea3m 1,2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 1 th\u00e1ng. </strong>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Barcelona h\u00f2a t\u1edbi 3 trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 80 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 31 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o trung b\u00ecnh 2,58 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m, Barcelona ch\u1ec9 ghi trung b\u00ecnh 1,37 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m 1,2 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d MU b\u1ecb C\u00f4ng Vinh lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay: Lee Nguy\u1ec5n, Denilson c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201ckh\u00f3c\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-22/1519307412-625-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d MU b\u1ecb C\u00f4ng Vinh lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay: Lee Nguy\u1ec5n, Denilson c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201ckh\u00f3c\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>CLB TP. HCM quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Rodrigo Possebon.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-23-2-gareth-bale-la-cai-gai-cua-real-c409a940533.html","id":"389"}]}